  <!-- About Section Content -->
  <section id="about">
    <h2>📜 About the Fish</h2>
    <p>
      "This fish doesn’t believe in borders. It thinks beyond limits, beyond oceans, beyond the ordinary.
      One day, it simply decided that the world was too small to stay in one place. So, it left the ocean and began its journey—no destination, just the thrill of exploring the unknown."
    </p>
    <p>
      "But there’s more to this fish than just curiosity. It thinks differently. It looked around and couldn’t find another fish that shared its vision—one that truly believed traveling the world was possible. While others swam in circles, following the currents they were told to follow, this fish wanted to create its own path."
    </p>
    <p>
      "It could have stayed. It could have followed. It could have worked under someone else’s rule. But why, when it has a mind of its own? Why, when it can build something far greater than just a small piece of the ocean? This fish doesn’t just want to explore—it wants to <strong>create its own empire.</strong>"
    </p>
    <p>
      "Who sent this fish on its journey? Maybe someone who questions everything. Maybe someone who believes in thinking beyond limits. Maybe someone who is already shaping something bigger. Or maybe… it’s you, the one reading this now."
    </p>
    <p>
      "There’s more behind these words. Stay tuned—you will soon get to know the real story of this fish. 🐟"
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Include Footer -->
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
